                  <content>
                     <AnchorPane prefHeight="180.0" prefWidth="200.0">
                        <children>
                           <TextArea editable="false" text="Q: How does Shinobu work? &#10;A: Shinobu is an app that allows you to rent movies/games. Simply download the app, browse the product library, select the item you want to rent, and click the ‘rent’ button.&#10;&#10;Q: How long can I rent a movie/game on Shinobu? &#10;A: The rental duration varies depending on the product. Please check each product rental’s duration before renting.&#10;&#10;Q: How do I check my current membership level?&#10;A: You can check your membership level by going to ‘Your Profile’, your current membership should be displayed on top of the page&#10;&#10;Q: How much does it cost to rent movies on Shinobu? &#10;A: The rental prices on Shinobu vary depending on the product. Prices are typically competitive and affordable.&#10;&#10;Q: What devices are compatible with Shinobu? &#10;A: Shinobu is available for download on both iOS and Android devices.&#10;&#10;Q: How do I return an item? &#10;A: Go to ‘Rentals’ tab, select/search for the product you want to return, click ‘Return’&#10;&#10;Q: What happens if I experience technical issues while using the app? &#10;A: In the rare event of technical issues, Shinobu provides customer support to assist you. You can reach out to our support team via the app, and we will promptly address any concerns you may have.&#10;&#10;Q: Does Shinobu offer any special promotions or discounts? &#10;A: Yes, Shinobu periodically offers special promotions, discounts, and exclusive deals for its users depends on their current membership.&#10;&#10;Q: How do I change my information? &#10;A: You can change your information by going into ‘Your Profile’" wrapText="true" AnchorPane.bottomAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.rightAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.topAnchor="0.0">
