                            <AnchorPane prefHeight="180.0" prefWidth="200.0">
                                <children>
                                    <TextArea editable="false" text="The year is 2023, in a small town called RMIT, five ambitious students came together with a shared passion for movies and technology. They envisioned a convenient way for movie/games lovers to access their favorite product without leaving the comfort of their homes. With their combined skills in programming, design, and entrepreneurship, they embarked on an exciting journey to create a  renting app that would change the way people enjoyed video/games.&#10;&#10;The journey began in a cramped class room, where the five friends spent countless late nights brainstorming and coding. They faced numerous challenges along the way, from technical glitches to limited resources, but their unwavering determination kept them going. They knew that their idea had the potential to revolutionize the entertainment rental industry.&#10;&#10;After months of hard work and perseverance, their vision materialized into a functioning renting app called &quot;Shinobu&quot;, offered a vast library of movies spanning different genres, from timeless classics to the latest blockbusters. Users could browse and rent movies/games/dvds with just a few taps on their smartphones or computers.&#10;&#10;Shinobu quickly gained popularity among the college community. Students were thrilled to have access to a wide range of movies and games at their fingertips. The app's user-friendly interface and seamless payment system made it a go-to platform for movie/game enthusiasts in the town.&#10;&#10;As word spread about Shinobu convenience and extensive movie/game collection, the app caught the attention of local media and investors. The five college students found themselves thrust into the limelight, juggling their studies and the demands of scaling their app. With the support of their professors and mentors, they navigated the challenges of scaling up their infrastructure and expanding their team to meet the growing user base.&#10;&#10;Shinobu's success was not limited to their town. The app gradually expanded its reach to neighboring cities and towns, captivating movie lovers everywhere. The team's dedication and innovative approach earned them accolades and recognition in the tech industry, inspiring other aspiring entrepreneurs.&#10;&#10;Today, Shinobu continues to thrive as a testament to the ambition and creativity of its founders.&#10;" wrapText="true" AnchorPane.bottomAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.leftAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.rightAnchor="0.0" AnchorPane.topAnchor="0.0">
